{"tid":828264,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真討論] 男仔點打扮先吸引到女仔","createTime":"2018-09-19T14:03:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T15:13:55.000Z","uid":113705,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"175cb66bd5cad3e780fd8e5255b6e10af19b8bb0","tid":828264,"uid":113705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T14:03:40.000Z","msg":"所謂人靠衣裝, 之前FB睇片D女仔話鍾意男仔著恤衫, 感覺乾淨D, 又有人話男仔就咁白T已經夠。究竟男仔應該著D咩先吸引到女仔, 起碼D女仔會覺得佢識打扮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋你地覺得應唔應該戴眼鏡??<br />\n係女仔既就快D入黎比下意見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申平時唔會專登去打扮, 求其T-shirt 短褲就出街。跟住好多fd都叫我打扮下自己，唔好成日咁求其，如果唔系出唔到pool <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP.S.假設正常樣,正常身高,<br />\n所以你地唔好又打埋D有錢或者靚仔就搞掂"},{"pid":"641ca8043ab7cfb886ee365ef716d0da4319347a","tid":828264,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T14:04:59.000Z","msg":"同你條毒丁講都晒氣"},{"pid":"98915d99e0ffb2512176da454cda73699f5c45ff","tid":828264,"uid":24938,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T14:07:17.000Z","msg":"其實髮型都好重要 唔好成堆草咁"},{"pid":"d7b561aa02cd792a5ed6cf3701f8c1edd7f41312","tid":828264,"uid":29070,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T14:07:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/19/220720_56341bcee1991a14e3f0b279279c6e35.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F220720_56341bcee1991a14e3f0b279279c6e35.png&h=9f3c18d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a07920d544e098aec73727da77331041bf520ad8","tid":828264,"uid":156326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T14:09:10.000Z","msg":"乾淨低調啦 我諗"},{"pid":"6d2a18b9ca85996e70aa771ee325d8d9152b9dbd","tid":828264,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy"